title: For Sale:  Sig Sauer Mosquito
postcontent: Used Sig Mosquito 22lr handgun for sale. Two toned and well cared for and is the later model with an F serial number.  This gun is patterned after the P226 and is only 10% smaller so in your hand this gun feels like a compact 9mm not a little toy like so many 22 guns. The breakdown for cleaning is just rotating one lever. I bought the gun used and it had a gritty trigger and I had ftf almost every magazine. The trigger is now smooth and I have had no failure to feeds with the mini mags I usually shoot or with a box of Remington Golden Bullets. It is now far superior to a new one in my opinion. The sale includes the gun, one magazine, two additional front sights of different heights to customize the gun to you and your ammo, the paperwork, the heavy recoil spring, the safety lockout key, and of course the all important cable lock.
